<def>Furious; mad; angry; fierce.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Then
wexeth wood and <xex>yond</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
